title: Brandon Coleman Sound Bank
text: The Brandon Coleman Signature Sound Bank features 50 killer patches created by the brilliant US keyboardist/producer Brandon Coleman (Kamasi Washington, Thundercat, Flying Lotus, Childish Gambino).

title: Dave Mackay Sound Bank
text: We are excited to offer an exclusive patch collection for Nord Stage 3 created by the brilliant Dave Mackay. The sound bank features 25 signature patches including powerful arpeggios, punchy pop pianos, ambient EPs and evolving pads.

title: Docskim Sound Bank
text:
Docskim Signature Sound Bank for Nord Stage 3 contains a wide selection of sounds - inspired by neo soul, hip hop, jazz, gospel, film scores, video game soundtracks.
Cinematic pianos, smooth and funky EPs, phat basses, warm pads, soaring leads and more.

title: J3PO Sound Bank
text: Brilliant patches for Nord Stage 3 from Julian "J3PO" Pollack. Incorporates electronic genres, progressive soul, experimental hip-hop and 80s synth-wave and features lo-fi sounds with vinyl crackle and tape hiss, retro analog synths and ambient patches.

title: Michael Bereal Sound Bank
text:
Signature Sound Bank crafted by the legendary gospel keyboardist and producer, Michael Bereal, featuring electric and acoustic pianos, layers, synth brass, and analog synths.

Twenty-five distinctive patches based on the Nord Stage 3 factory sounds.

title: Mike Patrick Sound Bank
text: Sound Bank for Nord Stage 3 - from the gifted British keyboardist/producer Mike Patrick. The Sound Bank incorporates influences of RnB, modern Pop and House music featuring beautiful vintage synths, vibey brass and orchestral strings.

title: Ondre J Pivec EPs (Stage 3)
text:
Grammy Award-winning keyboardist, composer, recording artist and bandleader Ondre J Pivec has created brilliant EP patches for Nord Stage 3.

From classic "bread and butter” to creamy, fat and barky EP sounds inspired by musical heroes and jazz legends.

title: Amber Upright
text: Large upright of German descent with an elegant, warm clear tone.

title: Baby Upright
text: A compact short scale piano of Swedish descent, with a very distinct character.

title: Ballad EP1
text: The Ballad EP1 piano layer has a brilliant, rich character and is based on classic sounds from the 80's.

title: Ballad EP2
text: The Ballad EP2 piano layer has a brilliant, rich character and is based on classic sounds from the 80's.

title: Bambino Upright
text: The Bambino Upright is a charming little instrument with a warm and shimmering sound.

title: Black Upright
text: The Black Upright is a Petrof 132 upright - a tall piano and typically used for musical schools, in clubs and homes.

title: BlueSwede Upright
text: The BlueSwede Upright is a tall upright of Swedish origin - prepared with the objective to keep its unique personality.

title: Bright Grand
text: Bright Grand Piano with a transparent character, expressive dynamic range and a crisp, rich tone.

title: Broadwood Fortepiano by Chris Maene
text: This fortepiano featured 6 octaves C-C and has more the character of a grand piano than the earlier fortepianos.

title: Concert Grand Ambient
text: This ambient recording represents the ideal setup for capturing the exquisite tones of a concert grand piano during classical performances.

title: Concert Grand Close
text: 9-foot concert grand, recorded with close-up microphone positioning, offers an immersive and intimate sound.

title: DigiGrand 1
text:
Vintage digital piano sampled with full velocity mapping to capture the unique dynamic response of the original sound.

Released August 2017

title: DigiGrand 2
text:
Vintage digital piano sampled with full velocity mapping to capture the unique dynamic response of the original sound.

Released August 2017

title: DX Full Tines
text: FM-based Electric Piano with a brillant, rich character and was one of the defining sounds in popular music during the 80's and 90's.

title: DX Rubba Tines
text: This FM-based Electric Piano sound was sampled from the legendary DX syntheziser, and emulates the sound of a vintage electric piano.

title: Electric Grand Amped
text: This Electric Grand was recorded through a magic mix of custom built pre-amps, tube amps and vintage outboard.

title: Electric Grand CP80
text: The legendary portable Electric Grand from the 70's and 80's.

title: Electric Grand Gerbstedt
text: This is a one of a kind custom modified Gerbstadt acoustic grand piano fitted with CP-80 pick-ups.

title: EP1 MK I, Low Deep
text: Late MK I built in May 1978 and adjusted to "deep timbre". The amplitude is set to "Low" to give the piano more fundamental.

title: EP2 MK I Suitcase, Close Ideal
text: Mk I Suitcase built in January 1975 - with optimized mechanics and adjusted the tines to "ideal timbre". The volume adjustment is "close".

title: EP3 MK II, Shallow Close
text: Mk II Stage Piano built in April 1981 and adjusted to ''shallow timbre''. This sound has loads of harmonics and bark.

title: EP4 MK V, Ideal Close
text: Mark V Stage 73 built in June 1984 and adjusted to ''ideal timbre''. The volume adjustment is ''close''.

title: EP5 MK I Suitcase, Bright Tines
text: 1975 mk I Suitcase with a special selection of hard hammer tips in certain ranges. Adjusted with "close miking" and set to ideal timbre.

title: EP6 Sparkletop Vintage '67
text: This Sparkletop is a real vintage beauty from 1967 and was recently refurbished in the US with new felt-hammers. The timbre is set to "ideal".

title: EP7 Tines Amped
text: This MK1 was recorded through a magic mix of custom built pre-amps, tube amps and vintage outboard.

title: EP8 Nefertiti MKI
text: The Nefertiti MKI is a funky old workhorse that has spent most of its days in the darkest corners of the legendary Nefertiti jazz club in Gothenburg.

title: EP9 Stockholm
text: A classic 1976 Mark I Stage EP, delivering a fat, round bottom with balanced bells, and a more barky and shallow sound when hit hard.

title: Felt Upright
text: A medium sized upright piano fitted with felt between the hammers and strings to provide a soft, warm and delicate piano sound.

title: French Harpsichord 1A Lower 8
text: This triple stringed harpsichord was recorded at the Swedish National Radio.

title: French Harpsichord 1B Upper 8
text: This triple stringed harpsichord was recorded at the Swedish National Radio.

title: Fairlight Collection
text: The Fairlight™ collection gives Nord users access to the legendary sounds from the early eighties. These sounds were sampled from an overhauled System IIx  with a detailed mapping to capture the original sound character of the sounds.

title: Mellotron Essential Collection
text: This collection includes 63 of the most well-known and classic sounds from the original Mellotron sound library. These sounds were created using fresh tapes that had been printed from the original masters - utilized in a new Mellotron mkVI,  state-of-the-art technology and original unused stock tape heads.

title: Mellotron Master Tapes - Artist Collection
text: In the abandoned Mellotron storage facility in Birmingham, a number of extremely rare tapes were discovered. These sounds were custom made for bands like Roxy Music, Yes, Jack Bruce, Genesis, Tangerine Dream and Black Sabbath specially created for use on stage, covering both leads and sound effects.

title: Mellotron Master Tapes - Rhythm Fills Collection
text: The Mellotron Rhythms and Fills produce charming sounds that are sure to bring a smile to your face. The Mellotron Rhythms and Fills were originally designed to allow anyone to sound like a professional musician with minimal effort.

title: Spitfire String Quintet
text: The Spitfire String Quintet is a world class collection full of character and detail, covering all essential articulations. With its unique authentic and intimate sound, the Spitfire String Quintet adds a new palette of high-end samples to the Nord Sample Library.

title: Swing!
text: The phenomenal Swing Collection contains lively big bands, brilliant ensemble strings and authentic upright basses - a premium selection of samples from the acclaimed libraries by ProjectSAM.

title: Symphobia
text: The Symphobia Strings collection contains a unique selection of outstanding symphonic strings from true ensemble recordings of a full symphony orchestra. One of the finest and most authentic symphonic strings libraries available.

title: Grand Lady D

title: Hohner Clavinet D6
